ws.rocket.path.meta

Interface Restrictable


  • public interface Restrictable
    Contract for tree values wishing to limit access to them and their descendant objects.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean isAvailable(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request)
      Reports whether the object is available for delivering or handling the request.

    • Method Detail

      • isAvailable

        boolean isAvailable(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request)
        Reports whether the object is available for delivering or handling the request. The return value does not have to depend on the request object.

        As an example, when false is returned:

        • for anonymous users, a login page could be served;
        • for authenticated users, an access denied page could be served.
        Parameters:
        request - The request being handled.
        Returns:
        A Boolean that is true when the request can be handled by the object (including its descendants in tree) implementing this contract
